{"name":"新的 Agent 能力升级","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"IMG_KEY_TODO","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","corner_radius":"8px","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**:GoGoGo: 无论是专业数据分析、高级图表生成，还是复杂问卷搭建，AI 都能帮你完成**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 生成问卷**\n不止于生成，AI 将深入洞察业务场景，自主规划问题、显示逻辑和设置，让专业问卷在对话间即刻交付","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"bitableform_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 问数**\n查数据、看指标、做分析。只需一句提问，即可获得专业的数据统计与分析结果，并清晰呈现分析过程。","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"sheet-line_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"4px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"**AI 生成仪表盘组件**\n通过对话让 AI 生成专业图表组件，桑基图、矩形树图、热力图、瀑布图等高级图表任你探索，支持下钻查看明细，体验比肩原生组件","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"vote_outlined","color":"blue"}}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"4px 4px 4px 6px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 4px 0px 4px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"更多能力与使用技巧，可查看下方帮助文档 👇","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"了解 AI 生成问卷"},"type":"primary","width":"fill","size":"medium","behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/989015423277?from=in-base","pc_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/989015423277?from=in-base","ios_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/989015423277?from=in-base","android_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/989015423277?from=in-base"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1},{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"了解 AI 问数"},"type":"primary","width":"fill","size":"medium","behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/777652685061-%E5%9F%BA%E4%B